00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Most traders don't lose because of bad ideas.
They lose in bad execution.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:10,000
You scan charts, second-guess entries,
and by the time you act, the move is gone.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:18,000
This bot scans for high-quality breakouts,
scores them, and prioritizes what matters.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:25,000
It checks trend, sector strength, and conviction,
then sends alerts directly to Discord.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:32,000
